# Request a nav_mode change. mode_manager gates entry (unknown mode, unmet car
# conditions) and answers accepted=false with a reason instead of switching.
# The new mode is announced on the latched nav_mode topic, not in this response.
string mode           # requested navigation mode, e.g. "follow", "stopped"
---
bool accepted         # true = mode is now active (or already was)
string message        # rejection reason, or an echo of the accepted transition
